{
  "texts": [
    "Sentiment analysis using attentional mechanisms 39, pretrained language models 40 and hybrid neural networks 41 has become popular recently.",
    "Despite notable achievements in both fake review detection and user preference analysis, several critical gaps remain unaddressed.",
    "(1) Lack of detection for AI-generated user reviews.",
    "Traditional fake review detection methods focus primarily on human-written fake reviews and rely on linguistic or behavioral patterns that are less effective when they are applied to AI-generated content.",
    "AI-generated reviews exhibit high fluency and contextual coherence, making their detection by existing approaches more challenging."
  ]
}